    id: 7,
    title: "Participatory Rural Appraisal (PRA) in Brgy. Dagatan, Dolores, Quezon",
    content: "The Participatory Rural Appraisal (PRA) was held in Barangay Dagatan, Dolores, Quezon, on March 30, 2022. The expert in PRA and also the consultant for the project, Dr. Macandog, guided the team on how to execute the FGD properly. The objective of the activity was to know the causes of pollution in the lake, the aquatic organisms that can be found in the lake, the solutions to the present problems that the community is facing, and many other related situations that happened in the community. \r\n\t\r\nLocal residents served as the primary information source, providing firsthand. The timeline mapping was the first activity held, followed by the community-based map, then causal mapping, and lastly the SWOT analysis. By analyzing the data from these methods, the present problems can be solved by having future policies that can be beneficial to the community.",
